# -------- Piper bundle rules --------
# Ignore everything under third_party/piper by default…
third_party/piper/**

# …but allow these specific ARM64 artifacts we want to ship:
!third_party/
!third_party/piper/
!third_party/piper/linux-arm64/
!third_party/piper/linux-arm64/piper
!third_party/piper/linux-arm64/libonnxruntime.so
!third_party/piper/linux-arm64/libpiper_phonemize.so*
# If you ship specific model files, unignore them explicitly:
!third_party/piper/models/
!third_party/piper/models/en_US-ryan-medium.onnx
!third_party/piper/models/en_US-ryan-medium.onnx.json

# never bundle test memory
data/memory.json
